{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PowerSlave Exhumed is a KEX Engine port of the classic console game perfectly blending both the PlayStation &amp; Saturn versions</h2><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678430/extras/bug_blast.gif?t=1717158599\" /><br><br><br><strong>New Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Widescreen / HD Display<br></li><li>Modern gamepad support<br></li><li>SMAA Antialiasing<br></li><li>Anisotropic texture filtering<br></li><li>Achievements<br></li><li>Vulkan / DirectX 11 graphics API<br></li><li>Smooth object interpolation for high refresh rate monitors<br></li><li>Both versions of the original game combined to bring the best of both worlds</li></ul><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678430/extras/Bastet_blast.gif?t=1717158599\" /><br><br><strong>Classic Description:</strong><br><br>Destination: The ancient Egyptian city of Karnak. Alien forces possessing horrifying powers have sealed off the once thriving community from all outside contact. As a covert operations specialist, you have been trained for all forms of contingencies. Nothing can prepare you, however, for the nightmare you are about to enter...<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>First Person Viewpoint Action<br></li><li>20 Plus Levels of Non-stop gameplay through an ancient Egyptian city and the tomb of the Pharaoh Ramses<br></li><li>Real time fully 3D rendered gameplay allows you to move between floors within a single level<br></li><li>Cross bridges and swim through underwater grottos<br></li><li>With just a machete to start, search for 6 other weapons including hand grenades, a flame thrower, an M-60 machine gun, and a magical cobra staff.<br></li><li>Dynamic lighting creates stunning visual effects.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678430/extras/ding_flame.gif?t=1717158599\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678430/extras/logo-2015_small.png?t=1717158599\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"King Of The World","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1678430/222f171cbd500499de937486f143c2691447400d.jpg"},{"name":"Life In Ruins","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1678430/017fb2918cc8e26a0f00790736126a1578841078.jpg"},{"name":"Tomb Raider","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1678430/7cfbf4582c7a9a5af3c41483879d36274b0051ac.jpg"},{"name":"Treasure Hunter Extraordinaire","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1678430/c2b015645b4598596645e487f73d1169844b5d11.jpg"},{"name":"Walk Like An Egyptian","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1678430/cbd9462cb39df814e0f22dc0c6eadaac7c710919.jpg"},{"name":"Aqua Lungs","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1678430/2dfe2bb9b87ab5f3e04d3c879a20e578f2b1ac50.jpg"},{"name":"Float like a Feather","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1678430/2a56a07f91f0f3979ec53e9c90707aeaa6f07a96.jpg"},{"name":"Achilles Heel No More","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1678430/abe700b02828a7c1e7f5dee8a50f22e3ef1bd3dd.jpg"},{"name":"What's Yours is Mine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1678430/f57980ac5d8cb432e884fff7a20f9cbf28cd8b13.jpg"},{"name":"Light as a Feather","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1678430/c18977a8c3ab070f3c567cf57b7031150b8d085c.jpg"}],"total":20},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1678430/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1717158599","bac